 The former Countdown star donned a dashing white jumpsuit with a statement gold belt accentuating her curves, as she revealed she was heading to an event of royal proportions. However, her dazzling look proved divisive in her comments section as Simon.owen.100 said: “Looking like one of Charlie's Angels.” Scott.dawkins.75 disagreed, writing that instead she "looks like Evel Knievel!” A large majority seemed to agree on one particular musician that Carol was imbuing, as Steffano_baldamani put it: “Elvis has entered the race course.” The 62-year-old was joined by a fleet of top British names as she appeared at Sandown Park Racecourse to watch Grand Military Gold Cup day.